title: Your Worst Nightmare - Season 2
description:
Your Worst Nightmare - Season 2

Your Worst Nightmare is a typical ID show where each episode includes commentary from law enforcement, criminal justice professionals, and friends and family of the victims. The show brings up real chilling crimes that have happened in the past.

Ep 1 - Bump In The Night
Ep 2 - Murder House
Ep 3 - Unexpected Company
Ep 4 - While She Was Sleeping
Ep 5 - There's No Place Like Home
Ep 6 - Psycho For Love
Ep 7 - Neighbor From Hell
Ep 8 - Fight Or Flight
Ep 9 - High School Revenge
Ep 10 - The Devil Went Down To Georgia
